WEBVTT

00:00:25.104 --> 00:00:26.983
HAYOM YOM SHLISHI

00:00:26.983 --> 00:00:30.755
HAESRIM VETESHA ELEF TSHAMEOT BEOKTOBER TISHIM VESHESH

00:00:30.755 --> 00:00:33.750
TET ZAYN CHESHVAN TAF SHIN NIN ZAYIN

00:00:33.750 --> 00:00:39.260
SHMI TOBY REISS-RUBIN VEANI ORECHET RAYON IM NADIA HOROWITZ LEBET HOROWITZ

00:00:39.260 --> 00:00:41.367
BAIR BNE BRAK YISRAEL.

00:00:45.438 --> 00:00:52.335
OKAY EH HAYOM YOM SHLISHI HAESRIM VETESHA BEOKTOBER ELEF TSHAMEOT TISHIM VESHESH, CHAF ZAYIN CHESHVAN

00:00:52.391 --> 00:00:54.445
TAF SHIN NUN ZAYIN

00:00:54.534 --> 00:00:56.520
EH TET ZAYIN CHESHVAN

00:00:57.369 --> 00:01:03.726
EH VESHMI TOBY REISS-RUBIN VEANI ORECHET RAYON IM NADIA HOROWITZ BEBNEI BRAK YISRAEL.

00:01:07.562 --> 00:01:09.295
SHALOM GVERET HOROWITZ.

00:01:09.536 --> 00:01:12.535
EH kent men zogn vos iz ayer nomen, bite?

00:01:12.877 --> 00:01:14.526
NADJA Horovits.

00:01:14.616 --> 00:01:16.206
un fun di shtub?

00:01:14.750 --> 00:01:16.241
ikh heys Nekhe

00:01:16.241 --> 00:01:18.644
Horovits, ober me ruft mikh NADJA.

00:01:18.716 --> 00:01:21.051
Horovits fun di heym, un haynt

00:01:21.051 --> 00:01:23.301
khasene gehat oykh mit a Horovits.

00:01:23.441 --> 00:01:24.533
a mishpokhe.

00:01:24.453 --> 00:01:26.642
ven zent ir geboyrn un vu?

00:01:26.512 --> 00:01:29.511
dray un tsvontsikstn in s- yuli

00:01:29.702 --> 00:01:33.815
nayntsn zibn un tsvontsik, in Pabyanits, dos iz nebn Lodzh.

00:01:34.562 --> 00:01:37.611
iz zent ir haynt vifl yor alt?

00:01:38.358 --> 00:01:40.277
vi alt zent ir haynt?

00:01:40.232 --> 00:01:41.206
ikh bin haynt

00:01:41.345 --> 00:01:42.876
bay di zibetsik yor.

00:01:43.303 --> 00:01:43.838
OKAY.

00:01:43.927 --> 00:01:47.736
ir vilt mir zogn dem nomen fun ayer foter un fun ayer muter?

00:01:46.661 --> 00:01:50.185
Yitskhok Arye Horovits,

00:01:50.185 --> 00:01:52.799
un mayn mame Tsirl Feyge Horovits.

00:01:52.905 --> 00:01:54.649
Goldtsoyber fun der heym.

00:01:54.649 --> 00:01:56.916
undz ze'mir geven tsvelef kinder,

00:01:57.258 --> 00:01:59.835
zeks yinglekh un zeks meydlekh.

00:02:00.380 --> 00:02:03.176
finef zenen geven geheyrat forn krig,

00:02:03.485 --> 00:02:10.275
un yare tsvey un fertsik, bay di oyszidlung, zenen mayne eltern gevezn mayn mame tsvey un fuftsik

00:02:10.275 --> 00:02:13.082
un mayn foter varshayndlekh dray un fuftsik.

00:02:14.555 --> 00:02:18.684
ir vilt mir zogn di nemen fun ayer sh- briders un shvesters?

00:02:18.048 --> 00:02:20.906
yo, ikh hof az ale nemen eb ikh gedenken.

00:02:20.906 --> 00:02:24.777
di ershte iz Pese Horovits

00:02:24.815 --> 00:02:26.666
geheyratet mit Maroko.

00:02:26.705 --> 00:02:28.404
di tsveyte hot geheys-

00:02:27.482 --> 00:02:29.080
zi hot gehat kinder?

00:02:29.068 --> 00:02:30.987
hot gehat dray kinder.

00:02:31.582 --> 00:02:33.416
di tsveyte hot gehat

00:02:33.793 --> 00:02:38.312
tsvey kinder, hot geheysn Zlatele, hot khasene gehat oykh mit a Horovits,

00:02:38.312 --> 00:02:39.795
mit a mishpokhe.

00:02:40.053 --> 00:02:41.735
der ku- mit a ershtn kuzin.

00:02:41.741 --> 00:02:47.103
di drite hot geheysn Sortshe, un hot khasene gehat mit Vaynberg

00:02:48.609 --> 00:02:51.104
un di ferde hot khasene gehat, Freyde

00:02:51.104 --> 00:02:53.700
Freyde, un hot khasene gehat mit Vaysgol.

00:02:54.363 --> 00:02:58.746
un dan iz gevezn a yingl, hot er geheysn Meyer.

00:02:59.595 --> 00:03:02.290
Hershl, ales Horovits

00:03:02.885 --> 00:03:07.521
un, un der driter

00:03:07.847 --> 00:03:10.036
Hersh, Meyer, Nosn

00:03:10.445 --> 00:03:12.263
neyn, Nosn iz geven di yingste.

00:03:13.162 --> 00:03:17.201
un dan bin ikh gevezn, un dan iz geven nokh dray unter mir.

00:03:17.201 --> 00:03:20.262
Moyshe, Srolik, NATAN.

00:03:21.836 --> 00:03:24.220
ir zent geven di zekste, dos

00:03:23.760 --> 00:03:25.696
ikh bin geven di naynte.

00:03:25.116 --> 00:03:26.626
di naynte, huh.

00:03:26.004 --> 00:03:26.674
yo.

00:03:27.219 --> 00:03:30.319
dray yinglekh far mir, un dray yinglekh nokh mir.

00:03:29.480 --> 00:03:30.369
nokh

00:03:32.855 --> 00:03:36.090
 in voser UNK hot der tate gearbet?

00:03:35.724 --> 00:03:37.113
mayn foter hot ge-

00:03:37.113 --> 00:03:40.950
akhtsn yor nokh di khasene hot er gelernt, hot bakumen kest.

00:03:41.090 --> 00:03:44.437
mayn mame iz geven eyn eyntsike tokhter, hot gehat tsvey zinen

00:03:44.437 --> 00:03:50.181
un mayn foter hot akhtsn yor bakumen kest un nokh dem iz er arayn

00:03:49.173 --> 00:03:52.492
ir vilt undz zogn vos hey- vos dos meynt kest?

00:03:52.346 --> 00:03:53.185
bite?

00:03:52.582 --> 00:03:55.670
ir vilt undz dertseyln vos mey- vos meynt men kest?

00:03:55.502 --> 00:04:00.239
kest, dos heyst er iz gezitsn gelernt, un der zeyde hot im oysgehaltn.

00:04:00.345 --> 00:04:02.686
un m'hot gehat a groyse WOHNUNG.

00:04:02.707 --> 00:04:07.174
farheltnsmesik oyf poylishe badingungen. m'hot dortn gevoynt mit tsvelef kinder

00:04:07.348 --> 00:04:08.625
un

00:04:07.888 --> 00:04:09.994
tsuzamen mit di bobe zeyde?

00:04:08.985 --> 00:04:15.623
neyn. di bobe zeyde hobn gehat a hoyz oyf z- a andere gas, ober undz zey hobn gedungen do di WOHNUNG, un

00:04:10.079 --> 00:04:10.740
neyn.

00:04:15.623 --> 00:04:17.941
m'hot do gevoynt, un

00:04:18.907 --> 00:04:24.269
nokh di akhtsn yor iz er arayn in gesheft. mayn zeyde hot gehat

00:04:24.324 --> 00:04:27.424
a oysarbaytung fun shtof in a farkoyf.

00:04:28.307 --> 00:04:31.643
geheysn UNK MANUFAKTURY in Lodzh.

00:04:32.171 --> 00:04:34.225
dos gesheft iz geven in Lodzh?

00:04:33.622 --> 00:04:38.528
neyn, tsvishn Pabyanits un Lodzh iz geven di fabrik, un dos gesheft iz geven in Lodzh oyf di

00:04:39.140 --> 00:04:42.932
oyf di ikh hob gevust frier. kh'hob fargesn.

00:04:43.005 --> 00:04:46.460
un di bey- zeyde bobe hobn oykh gevoynt in Pabyanits?

00:04:45.857 --> 00:04:51.946
zey hobn oykh gevoynt in Pabyanits. mayn mame iz geborn in Lodzh, zey zenen geven fun Lodzh, ober azoy az di fabrik iz gevorn

00:04:51.946 --> 00:04:55.049
noent tsu Pabyanits hot men zikh getsoygn nokh Pabyanits.

00:04:55.948 --> 00:05:00.195
ir kent mir fartseyln in v- in velkhe shul ir hot gelernt?

00:04:59.171 --> 00:05:04.667
ikh bin geganen in a shule numer draytsn hot es geheysn. s'iz gevezn yidishe kinder, a

00:05:04.790 --> 00:05:06.289
folkshule.

00:05:06.289 --> 00:05:10.456
yinglekh mit meydlekh, bazunder gezitsn, ober m'iz geven in eyn KITA

00:05:11.422 --> 00:05:12.649
un

00:05:11.850 --> 00:05:14.708
bloyz yidishe kinder hobn gelernt UNK?

00:05:13.599 --> 00:05:18.386
nor yidishe kinder, un fun finef biz zibn iz men geganen in Beys Yankev.

00:05:18.797 --> 00:05:22.144
iz di shule gevezn far mitog, un nokh mitog farnakht

00:05:22.144 --> 00:05:24.951
iz men geganen oyf tsvey shule lernen LIMUDE KODESH.

00:05:25.428 --> 00:05:25.712
mh.

00:05:26.289 --> 00:05:28.860
velkhe shprakh hot ets geredt in di heym?

00:05:28.128 --> 00:05:31.247
m'hot in di heym geredt yidish un poylish.

00:05:31.247 --> 00:05:33.169
ober merstns yidish.

00:05:32.820 --> 00:05:33.946
yidish.

00:05:34.473 --> 00:05:40.746
ir kent ir dertseyln a bisl iber dos lebn in di mishpokhe, di shvester un di briders, vi azoy

00:05:39.401 --> 00:05:43.328
mh yo, m'hot, di shvestern hobn khasene gehat

00:05:43.400 --> 00:05:46.527
iz di eltste hot khasene gehat bin ikh gevezn nokh a kleyn

00:05:46.527 --> 00:05:49.369
meydl. kh'hob gehat a yor. m'hot mir gezogt az m'hot gemakht

00:05:49.475 --> 00:05:52.443
dem ⟨oysshteyn⟩ in di shtub hot men gemakht kleydlekh far mir

00:05:52.443 --> 00:05:56.321
ober dos gedenk ikh nisht, un dan di nekste khasene

00:05:57.373 --> 00:06:03.083
gedenk ikh oykh nisht, un di drite khasene iz men geforn, m'hot

00:06:03.083 --> 00:06:06.143
nokh Aleksander, vayl es iz geven ⟨Aleksandern⟩ rebn's

00:06:06.232 --> 00:06:12.996
a, a mishpokhe. mayn foter's bruder iz geven dortn a eydem Aleksander, un dan hot men undz hot meshadekh geven mit im

00:06:12.996 --> 00:06:14.277
s'a ershte kuzin

00:06:14.400 --> 00:06:20.837
iz men geforn in d- Aleksander, geven di khasene normal un di khasene iz bay di kale, ober azoy vi dos iz geven a rebishe khasene

00:06:20.837 --> 00:06:25.377
hot men gemakht di khasene in Aleksander ober me hot mikh nisht mitkumen, ikh bin fir tsi finef yor alt

00:06:25.377 --> 00:06:33.615
un un di ferde khasene gedenk ikh shoyn yo. bin ikh geven a meydele. m'hot mir gemakht a sheyn kleyd. bin shoyn gevezn

00:06:34.059 --> 00:06:37.007
un di shvester hobn gevoynt noent tsu enk?

00:06:36.050 --> 00:06:40.095
yo, di eltste shvester hot gevoynt a por hayzer fun undz

00:06:40.185 --> 00:06:45.664
un s'iz nisht keyn aza zeyer groyse yidishe gegnt. m'iz gevezn ZIEMLICH kontsentrirt

00:06:45.737 --> 00:06:50.508
un di GROSSE eltern, di bobeshi un zeydeshi, hobn gevoynt oyf di Varshavski, oykh nisht vayt.

00:06:51.828 --> 00:06:53.781
un ire

00:06:53.988 --> 00:07:00.952
z- di, s'iz geven, dos, d- dos lebn in di k- s'iz geven a groyse kehile a yidishe in Pabyanits?

00:06:59.692 --> 00:07:03.638
s'iz gevezn a groyse nor vifl veys ikh nisht, vayl

00:07:03.638 --> 00:07:06.404
ikh bin nisht azoy, gedenk nisht fun forn krig

00:07:06.425 --> 00:07:10.557
ober s'iz geven a sheyn yidish lebn. s'iz gevezn khsidishe shtiblekh un

00:07:10.557 --> 00:07:11.871
s'iz geven...

00:07:11.437 --> 00:07:15.145
bay enk iz geven a khasidishe mishpokhe?

00:07:13.327 --> 00:07:17.726
yo. undz ze'mir fun a Gerer s- mishpokhe. zeyer a khsidishe shtub.

00:07:17.951 --> 00:07:24.021
mayn foter hot yedn in di sh- fri gegebn daf yoymi shir in Gerer shtibl.

00:07:24.380 --> 00:07:28.881
un aleyn hot er gelernt nokh ven er iz shoyn arayn in BUSINESS hot er gelernt

00:07:29.038 --> 00:07:32.948
zeyer ZIEMLICH a sakh. biz eynse bay nakht, oyfgeshtanen far tog

00:07:33.290 --> 00:07:37.622
un dos yidishe lebn iz gevezn. s'iz geven a groys yidish kheyder

00:07:37.712 --> 00:07:40.772
un s'iz geven tsvey yidishe shuln, un

00:07:40.772 --> 00:07:43.225
azelkhe tsienistishe oykh, vos ikh veys nisht.

00:07:43.398 --> 00:07:47.106
s'iz geven a Aleksanderer shtibl, a Gerer shtibl, vos ikh veys.

00:07:46.875 --> 00:07:50.734
un ir zent gegangen in epes a organizatsye a yidishe, s'iz

00:07:49.524 --> 00:07:55.368
iz, shabes nokh mitog bin ikh geven in BATYA. bin nokh nisht geven in benos, vayl ikh bin nokh geven tsu yung

00:07:55.368 --> 00:07:57.115
un m'iz geganen shabes nokh mitog

00:07:57.115 --> 00:07:59.357
hern PARSHAT HASHAVUA, ober

00:08:00.392 --> 00:08:02.243
farshidene zakhn.

00:08:01.235 --> 00:08:03.580
ir hot gelernt IVRIT oykh farn krig?

00:08:03.530 --> 00:08:04.531
neyn.

00:08:04.531 --> 00:08:05.720
m'hot nisht gelernt kh-.

00:08:05.720 --> 00:08:08.874
kh'hob gehat a khaverte, un zi hot zikh gelernt privat, ober undz hot men nisht...

00:08:08.002 --> 00:08:11.119
in di shule hot men, in Beys Yankev nokh nisht.

00:08:08.998 --> 00:08:13.346
neyn. neyn, neyn. m'hot brokhes gelernt un

00:08:13.352 --> 00:08:16.182
davenen, ober nisht keyn IVRIT.

00:08:17.047 --> 00:08:24.163
un, ir gedenkt, dos sh- ets hot zikh di mey- di, di froyen hot ets oykh gedavnt in shtibl in Aleks-

00:08:23.308 --> 00:08:28.714
neyn. Gerer shtibl hot nisht gehat far keyn froyen, nor s'iz geven a shul oyf undzere gas

00:08:28.714 --> 00:08:31.886
un m'iz geganen shabes droshe mit

00:08:31.886 --> 00:08:35.031
geganen tsum davenen, di kinder zenen a sakh mol mitgeganen.

00:08:37.027 --> 00:08:37.967
mh.

00:08:38.123 --> 00:08:40.801
di briders hobn gelernt in kheyder?

00:08:40.065 --> 00:08:44.853
di brider hobn gelernt in kheyder, un zenen geven zeyer khsidishe bokherim

00:08:44.853 --> 00:08:49.103
un geforn oyf yontoyvim ts- nokh ger, di tsvey eltste.

00:08:49.397 --> 00:08:51.485
di foter iz oykh geforn?

00:08:51.523 --> 00:08:53.290
d- di foter ayere?

00:08:51.911 --> 00:08:55.528
mayn foter yo. mayn foter iz geven zeyer a sharfer Gerer khosid

00:08:55.528 --> 00:08:59.899
un iz geforn zeyer oft. er iz geven a mishpokhe fun Ger, un er iz geven zeyer noent

00:08:59.899 --> 00:09:01.272
tsum Gerer hoyf.

00:09:01.800 --> 00:09:02.453
mh.

00:09:02.677 --> 00:09:04.784
un ir

00:09:04.784 --> 00:09:08.697
 ir muter hot gearbet etvos?

00:09:07.470 --> 00:09:12.091
mayn mame hot nisht gearbet, ober zi hot klal zakhn, az m'hot gebroykht epes

00:09:12.091 --> 00:09:18.636
far oreme mentshn geyen nokh gelt, un tsuzametnemen epes iz zi geven shtendik greyt tsu helfn.

00:09:19.839 --> 00:09:24.525
m'hot geshpilt epes instrumentn bay enk emetser fun di kinder?

00:09:23.028 --> 00:09:26.721
yo, mayne kinder, mayne shvester hot geshpilt oyf a

00:09:26.721 --> 00:09:30.684
a fidl, nor vifl ver genoy, ober a por kinder hobn geshpilt.

00:09:30.555 --> 00:09:34.701
un ir hot gehat oykh epes als kind vos ir hot lib gehat?

00:09:31.820 --> 00:09:33.233
mayn zun...

00:09:33.272 --> 00:09:37.030
yo, man zun, tsu lange yorn, hot geshpilt zeyer gut fidl.

00:09:37.203 --> 00:09:41.113
vayl mir zenen dokh leviim, hot men es gehat in, zet zikh oys in blut.

00:09:43.177 --> 00:09:48.093
ir zent, s'iz geven fun di, fun di,

00:09:48.093 --> 00:09:56.165
beys YAKOV oder fun di BATYA vos ir zogt, s'iz geven oykh ah zumer aktivitetn, ir zent aroysgeforn oyf CAMPs oder aza

00:09:54.703 --> 00:09:59.794
ken zayn, ober ikh bin keyn mol nisht gevorn, vayl undz ze'mir geforn zumer aroys

00:09:59.985 --> 00:10:05.905
nebn Rusk oyf a tsvey khadoshim, azoy az ⟨undz⟩, bin keyn mol nisht geforn oyf keyn kolonyes.

00:10:04.068 --> 00:10:06.510
tsuzamen mit di gantse mishpokhe?

00:10:06.718 --> 00:10:10.426
tsuzamen mit di gantse mishpokhe zent ets aroysgeforn?

00:10:07.967 --> 00:10:12.755
di gantse mishpokhe iz geforn aroys oyf zumer, un

00:10:13.299 --> 00:10:16.905
in zeyer primitive badingungen, ober s'iz gevezn CHOFESH

00:10:17.366 --> 00:10:21.225
OHNE likht un OHNE vaser, ober s'iz geven zeyer gut.

00:10:21.804 --> 00:10:25.512
m'hot es zeyer ENJOYED in di badingungen vos iz gevezn.

00:10:26.698 --> 00:10:30.169
vi alt zent ir geven ven di krig hot oysgebrokhn?

00:10:30.714 --> 00:10:34.506
ven di krig hot oysgebrokhn, vi alt v- zent ir geven?

00:10:34.190 --> 00:10:39.804
yare tsvey un ferts- fuftsik, i- tsvey un fertsikstn iz zi geven tsvey un fertsik YEA- yor alt.

00:10:38.932 --> 00:10:42.150
di mame.

00:10:39.810 --> 00:10:42.144
iz in nayn, iz in nayn un fertsik

00:10:42.144 --> 00:10:43.703
yor gemuzt zayn ba-

00:10:42.780 --> 00:10:46.690
un SIE vi alt zenen SIE gevezn? draytsn.

00:10:44.433 --> 00:10:46.031
ikh bin geven draytsn.

00:10:47.218 --> 00:10:53.248
ir gedenkt, ir hot erinerungen AN antisemitizm vos iz geven bay enk

00:10:53.248 --> 00:10:56.022
als kind? ir hot gefilt antisemitizm?

00:10:56.347 --> 00:10:58.488
az s'iz k- az a krig geyt kumen

00:10:58.488 --> 00:11:01.019
ikh hob a sakh zakhn nisht farshtanen nokh vos

00:11:00.887 --> 00:11:03.194
ir gedenkt epes vos

00:11:01.019 --> 00:11:01.439
dos

00:11:02.017 --> 00:11:08.030
i- yo. m'iz gezitsn ven di bombes zenen gefaln, ven di krig iz oysgefang-

00:11:08.030 --> 00:11:11.817
un m- mayn shvester hot gevoynt oyfn parter, iz men geganen tsu ir

00:11:11.872 --> 00:11:17.807
un s'iz geven fraytik. yeder iz gezitsn un zi iz aroysgeganen. zi hot ongegreyt shabes, trots dem vos iz geven

00:11:18.285 --> 00:11:20.001
a bisl geferlekh, ober

00:11:20.563 --> 00:11:21.655
un

00:11:20.765 --> 00:11:22.694
ober farn krig

00:11:22.694 --> 00:11:28.708
hot ir geshpirt antisemitizm? ir hot gehat kontakt mit goyim? ir hot gevust epes?

00:11:27.043 --> 00:11:31.257
mh, neyn, kontakt mit goyim hot men spetsyel nisht gehat

00:11:31.397 --> 00:11:32.489
ober

00:11:33.725 --> 00:11:34.564
neyn.

00:11:34.400 --> 00:11:41.864
un es, ir hot ge-, ir hot, ir hot shoyn gekent farshteyn az se geyt kumen a krig, az se greyt zikh epes? me hot geredt fun dem in di heym?

00:11:40.104 --> 00:11:44.320
m'hot geredt, m'hot geredt az s'vet zayn a krig, ober kh'hob nisht farshtanen

00:11:44.320 --> 00:11:47.270
m'hot keyner nisht farshtanen az dos vet kumen aza krig

00:11:47.276 --> 00:11:52.688
az m'hot nisht gevolt esn hot men gezogt me muz oyfesn, vayl s'iz geven a mol der krig, iz nisht geven

00:11:52.727 --> 00:11:54.916
keyn broyt, keyn kartoflen

00:11:54.735 --> 00:11:57.490
m'hot gehat erinerungen AM friern krig.

00:11:55.038 --> 00:11:56.107
ober dos

00:11:56.107 --> 00:11:59.676
yo, veys ikh az shtendik az m'hot dertseylt a

